@swebarb

No offense but you are doing it wrong. I've personally used this and there are plenty of other people using the reloaded torrent and this crack that got it to work.

Read "lilwekim"'s post on http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7869515/Far_Cry_3-RELOADED

@Retsknub - Make a shortcut from 'Farcry.exe'

Then left click on the shortcut, and then properties. Add at the end of 'Target' ' -offline' (with a space in front).

Then put in all the stuff from this crack into the Reloaded crack, then play. Should work X)
